elements.title: Day 1: Edinburgh
elements.description: Start your journey in Scotland's historic capital. Explore the Royal Mile and visit the magnificent Edinburgh Castle.

elements.title: Day 2: Loch Ness
elements.description: Travel north into the Highlands to the famous Loch Ness. Enjoy the stunning scenery and keep an eye out for Nessie! You'll stay overnight in the nearby city of Inverness.

elements.title: Day 3: Isle of Skye
elements.description: Journey to the dramatic Isle of Skye. Explore the colorful harbor town of Portree and the island's stunning landscapes, like the Old Man of Storr and the Quiraing.

elements.title: Day 4: Glasgow
elements.description: Travel south to Glasgow, Scotland's largest city, known for its vibrant arts scene, architecture, and friendly locals.

elements.title: Route Day 2: Edinburgh to Loch Ness
elements.description: Driving from Edinburgh to Loch Ness.

elements.title: Route Day 3: Loch Ness to Isle of Skye
elements.description: Driving from Loch Ness to Portree on the Isle of Skye.

elements.title: Route Day 4: Isle of Skye to Glasgow
elements.description: Driving from the Isle of Skye to Glasgow.

elements.title: Route Day 5: Glasgow to Edinburgh
elements.description: A short drive to complete the loop back to Edinburgh.
